Final SQL query: SELECT h.name FROM Highschooler h JOIN Friend f ON h.ID = f.student_id OR h.ID = f.friend_id GROUP BY h.ID ORDER BY COUNT(f.student_id) + COUNT(f.friend_id) DESC LIMIT 1;
Final execution result: passed
