Final SQL query: SELECT D.name FROM Dogs AS D JOIN Owners AS O ON D.owner_id = O.owner_id JOIN Treatments AS T ON D.dog_id = T.dog_id GROUP BY D.name HAVING SUM(T.cost_of_treatment) <= 1000;
