Final SQL query: SELECT T1.breed_name FROM Breeds AS T1 INNER JOIN Dogs AS T2 ON T1.breed_code = T2.breed_code GROUP BY T1.breed_name ORDER BY COUNT(T2.dog_id) DESC LIMIT 1;
Final execution result: passed
